{"tid":1488040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有人集中支持澳門！文宣！輿論！咪撚再推咩假波母犬！！","createTime":"2019-08-19T13:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:18:04.000Z","uid":90601,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a820a55bb8ef2601cbf0eb9c4e737b05006b0b97","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68678997_115194633172511_40013049200902144_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQkprski-PtplCh158fHIEbNcjDRSyF64rmbg0E7uNQwUlEAdHRN-25E2wAIsHQT0hI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=541faa9a124366b4abe80c06b8d24d6f&amp;oe=5DCDED7D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68678997_115194633172511_40013049200902144_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQkprski-PtplCh158fHIEbNcjDRSyF64rmbg0E7uNQwUlEAdHRN-25E2wAIsHQT0hI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D541faa9a124366b4abe80c06b8d24d6f%26oe%3D5DCDED7D&h=b4c9794d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/macau.standwithHK/photos/a.109403393751635/115194629839178/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmacau.standwithHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.109403393751635%2F115194629839178%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ff4c924d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/macau.standwithHK/photos/a.109403393751635/115194629839178/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【請各位幫手share！！！】<br />\n噴水池白色恐怖！（綜合網上消息，持續更新，已fact check）<br />\n<br />\n．噴水池現有大量警察駐守<br />\n．警察針對穿黑衫市民，並要求查身份證，有多人向我們表示被查或目擊有人被查<br />\n☆ 有2至3名黑衫人士（圖中）被警方帶上警車<br />\n．被帶上警車的有一位短髮女士、一位帶帽人士、一位葡籍女士。<br />\n期間葡籍女士一直用英文與警方對話，但沒有得到回應，葡籍女士非常無奈地問現場有沒有人士識英文，但最後都被帶上警車。<br />\n．有消息指被帶走人是因為身上有貼紙<br />\n．RTHK消息：有個別穿了整套黑衣的年輕人，在晚上8時鐘聲响起時，由旁邊坐位起立默站，但不接受任何訪問。<br />\n<br />\n請注意：舉標語、叫口號有可能被視為非法示威<br />\n請記得：我無嘢講、我要見律師、我唔解鎖"},{"pid":"b6ba4cc5d58ec0696ba9a8c528b02cb126c4637a","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"企得出黎既就係手足！！港澳互保呀！"},{"pid":"1b760e8b9f29eafcea8346c1e314fbbdc27e7c67","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"206bd4ec0d309cf2bb2e9beff96f9c288addded2","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16f6d4a451e08759008048416966448aab9c17be","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"澳門原本有人發起今晚8時，到中區議事亭前地默站「反對港警使用過份武力」，聲援香港人，之後有人轉載發起人取消活動的消息。<br />\n<br />\n現場有個別穿了整套黑衣的年輕人，在晚上8時鐘聲響起時起立默站，但不接受任何訪問。<br />\n<br />\nRTHK"},{"pid":"e50a40ebc04416604ad77d1dd72f28ea2f539c15","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475582-20190819.htm?fbclid=IwAR1mIgzfZLVrlZ2IjAsW7IbJlIi9n92jqnIKh1_X461Y36PnOYenabRrEyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475582-20190819.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1mIgzfZLVrlZ2IjAsW7IbJlIi9n92jqnIKh1_X461Y36PnOYenabRrEyc&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=a6d5b1ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475582-20190819.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1mIgzfZLVrlZ2IjAsW7IbJlIi9n92jqnIKh1_X461Y36PnOYenabRrEyc&h=86c8e64b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475582-20190819.htm?fbclid=IwAR1mIgzfZLVrlZ2IjAsW7IbJlIi9n92jqnIKh1_X461Y36PnOYenabRrEyc</a>"},{"pid":"e3d4e306e87c55b1b35b162b1de22dcecccdd5e4","tid":1488040,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff73d47db5a1ce8e86466ed51fa8274b0f8624cb","tid":1488040,